      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "WELL KEPT SECRET (1) drew a squeeze box and was game in defeat when a close second, 1.5 lengths from the winner Gramercy Gift (20.94) at this track. Sure to be about the mark. CASE OF FATE (2) ran a good time (23.78) winning a Maiden two back at Wagga but missed the frame latest finishing fifth at Wagga. Well placed here and should do much better. HARRITA'S REBEL (8) comes off an average effort last start when sixth at Bulli over 340m behind Paw Berry (20.11) in a Grade 5. Was in the money the start prior. Cannot be taken lightly. MEL MONELLI (7) will be hard to beat despite making her debut at this trip.",
